%%{init: {'themeVariables': { 'background': '#ffffff' }}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant UI as DemoHttpServer
    participant MS as MediaStation
    participant Topic as media-topic
    participant B_LR as Blinds (LivingRoom)
    participant B_K as Blinds (Kitchen)

    Note over UI, B_K: User clicks "Play Movie" in the UI
    UI->>MS: Ask: PlayMovie(replyTo)
    
    alt Movie is already playing
        MS-->>UI: PlayMovieResponse(success=false, message="Already playing")
        Note right of UI: UI shows red error message
    else Movie not playing
        MS->>MS: Set moviePlaying = true
        MS->>Topic: Publish: MediaStationPlaying(playing=true)
        
        par Topic Broadcast
            Topic-->>B_LR: MediaStationPlaying(true)
            B_LR->>B_LR: updateBlindsState() (Close)
        and
            Topic-->>B_K: MediaStationPlaying(true)
            B_K->>B_K: updateBlindsState() (Close)
        end
        
        MS-->>UI: PlayMovieResponse(success=true, message="Movie started")
        Note right of UI: UI shows green success message
    end
